modName: Naldesia-a new world_Naldesia-un nuovo mondo BETA
summary: Work in progress mod including a new big worldspace. It is a big work to do and if someone wanted to become co-author of this mod and collaborate with me would be welcome.
descriptionHtml:
For now this is still a work in progress, I have just made the terrain with LOD and put just some statics

This mod will become a big worldspace with its actors, quests, wars, etc even depending how many people will want to help me, even little helps would be great, for example if you want just to create a dungeon and nothing more you can do it and send it to me, then I will merge it in my mod!

Now dawnguard isn\'t needed anymore

INSTALLATION
The readme which is in this mod page explains everything
author: Pelinal Whitestrake crusader
